      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">When Agents Are the Customer: The Machine Commerce Discovery Layer</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">Today, a human decides which vendor to work with. Tomorrow, an AI agent will make that evaluation. Autonomously. At scale. In seconds.</p>
